Additional trade‑in values require purchase of a new iPhone, subject to availability and limits. Must be at least 18. Apple or its trade-in partners reserve the right to refuse or limit any Trade&nbsp;In transaction for any reason. In‑store trade‑in requires presentation of a valid, government-issued photo&nbsp;ID (local law may require saving this information). Sales tax may be assessed on full value of new iPhone. Additional terms from Apple or Apple’s trade-in partners may apply. Monthly pricing: Available to qualified customers and requires 0% APR, 24-month installment loan with Citizens&nbsp;One or Apple&nbsp;Card&nbsp;Monthly&nbsp;Installments and iPhone activation with AT&amp;T, Sprint, T-Mobile, or Verizon. Taxes and shipping not included. Additional Apple&nbsp;Card&nbsp;Monthly&nbsp;Installments terms are in the <a href="https://www.goldmansachs.com/terms-and-conditions/Apple-Card-Customer-Agreement.pdf" rel="nofollow">Customer&nbsp;Agreement</a>.
